 scary noises and knock random doors..once one of ours room was getting knocked at night and it got closed on its own","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:44 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"😮"}]},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"So, we told the hostel warden and he called father to do some process..it was Christian school","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:44 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Ohhhh","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:45 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"That’s so freakkyyyyy","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:45 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Sir how old were you then?","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:45 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"13-14","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:45 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"😭 that would have been really scaryyy","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:46 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yupp..I was scared af","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:46 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"😢"}]},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"And when you think lot about these things we start getting delusional and whatever happens we think it must be because of that..so, were at that stage at that time","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:47 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I know, brain is the biggest enemy in these situation","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:48 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"And you should have seen the hostel..it had old architecture like it was some very old palace with long passage.. totally gothic","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:48 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yuppp","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:48 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"🥹😭","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:49 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I would feel my parents hated me if they left me somewhere like this","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:51 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Sorry","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:51 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"It's okay ...it's normal to feel that way","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:52 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I kept big grudge on them for just threatening me to put me in hostel","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:53 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I was like, Do you like this feeling of me being scared for being away from you","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:55 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"And developed this mindset that you should not need them","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:55 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"You were threatened too 🥺","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:56 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"All the time","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:57 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"You were, saved ma'am","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:58 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I am happy for you","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:58 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"And I feel for you sir , I am really happy that you were strong.","time":"Dec 18, 2023 6:59 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"It took time ..but I was okay...now I don't even get happy or sad when I am with them now..I am so used to being alone now","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:02 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"It's more like neutral thing for me?","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:03 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Right","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:03 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"That’s better","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:03 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"We are not mean to them either","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:03 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Just surviving","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:04 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"yupp","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:04 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Honestly I once thought I should blame them","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:04 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"And take out my anger on them","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:05 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"But right then I heard from mufti menk","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:05 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"That parents are as well part of the test in this world for us.","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:06 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yess.. rightI came to that understanding that there is no point in blaming them and holding grudges is actually sin","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:07 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"So, I was like I should move on ..they must have reasons for what they did","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:08 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"You are a good listener 😊","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:09 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"In a call now :(","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:10 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"},{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"And you are good at everything","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:13 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"😢"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"It’s fine sir","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:16 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"You can take your time","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:16 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I am back ma'am","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:28 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"When will you have dinner","time":"Dec 18, 2023 7:28 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I had a Chicken sandwich","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:07 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"What will you have ?","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:07 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I think it's chicken from afternoon and eggs","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:25 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Good","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:25 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"How you feeling ma'am","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:26 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Not sleepy yet","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:27 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"It's good.","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:27 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Have you ever done night before","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:28 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Never !!!!!!!!!!","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:30 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Okkay","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:30 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"You will be fine 😊","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:31 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"It's 10 and got another work :(","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:31 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"😡","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:32 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Tell them you won’t do","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:38 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Don’t do it sir","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:38 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I logged off","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:48 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Was having dinner ma'am","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:48 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"It was aaloo matar ki sabji","time":"Dec 18, 2023 8:51 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Did you leave ma'am?","time":"Dec 18, 2023 9:32 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"},{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I am leaving in a minute","time":"Dec 18, 2023 9:36 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Okkay","time":"Dec 18, 2023 9:39 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I have left","time":"Dec 18, 2023 9:49 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I got late 😭😭","time":"Dec 18, 2023 9:49 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"It's okay ma'am..no worries.","time":"Dec 18, 2023 9:50 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"It's the first day","time":"Dec 18, 2023 9:50 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"You in rickshaw now?","time":"Dec 18, 2023 9:52 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Yaaaa","time":"Dec 18, 2023 9:58 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"My sis and mum is anxious","time":"Dec 18, 2023 9:59 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"They will be","time":"Dec 18, 2023 9:59 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I am Lil bit too 😔","time":"Dec 18, 2023 10:00 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"But you will do fine that I know","time":"Dec 18, 2023 10:00 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Me too","time":"Dec 18, 2023 10:00 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I have reached","time":"Dec 18, 2023 10:01 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Okay ma'am","time":"Dec 18, 2023 10:01 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I’ll keep the phone sir","time":"Dec 18, 2023 10:05 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Bye","time":"Dec 18, 2023 10:05 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Bye 😭","time":"Dec 18, 2023 10:05 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Please have something when u feel like. Don't stress much. You will be okay..and take care of yourself please 🥺","time":"Dec 18, 2023 10:06 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I will be there","time":"Dec 18, 2023 10:33 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I am having slight headache but rest is fine","time":"Dec 18, 2023 12:40 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Do sleep well","time":"Dec 18, 2023 12:41 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Allah hafiz","time":"Dec 18, 2023 12:41 pm","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","t